  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2007-02-08",
    "date": "2007-03-21T14:59:43Z",
    "text": "Clean Air Sustainability Act of 2007 - Amends the Clean Air Act to revise the definition of a \"major source\" of hazardous air pollutants to specify that a source's \"potential to emit\" refers to its maximum capacity to emit a pollutant on the date the source is required to comply with a national emission standard, without regard to any lower subsequent emission levels of that pollutant attributable to compliance with such standard or other factors."
